sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User (UI/BFF)
    participant P as auth-api (:7011)
    participant K as Keyset (kid-resolved)
    participant R as Redis (JTI denylist)

    U->>P: POST /v1/oauth/token grant_type=refresh_token
    P->>K: verify RS256 under resolved kid
    P->>R: GET denylist(old JTI)
    alt JTI present (replay)
        P-->>U: 401 invalid_grant
        Note over P,R: replay detected — token chain compromised
    else fresh
        P->>R: SET denylist(old JTI), TTL = remaining lifetime
        P->>K: sign new access (30 min) + new refresh (30d sliding)
        P-->>U: rotated access + refresh
    end
